OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPetr√≥polis: Hopes fade for
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsurvivors in flood-hit     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FBrazil city                
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Alarms rang out across the Brazilian   
OL,6, city of Petropolis on Thursday, warning
OL,7, of more heavy rain to come after floods
OL,8, and landslides killed at least 117     
OL,9, people with more than 100 missing.     
OL,11,FThe rescue mission has been temporarily
OL,12,Fcalled off and some people, fearing    
OL,13,Fmore destruction, are fleeing the city.
OL,15,FOne volunteer rescuer said that finding
OL,16,Fsurvivors under the rubble was now     
OL,17,F"practically impossible".              
OL,19,FThis week's rainfall in Petropolis was 
OL,20,Fthe heaviest in nearly a century.      
